"navigating tabs
map <C-h> <C-w>h
map <C-j> <C-w>j
map <C-k> <C-w>k
map <C-l> <C-w>l
map <C-left> <C-w>h
map <C-down> <C-w>j
map <C-up> <C-w>k
map <C-right> <C-w>l

" Center on next/previous search result
nnoremap n nzzzv
nnoremap N Nzzzv

" Scroll half-page and center cursor
nnoremap <C-d> <C-d>zz
nnoremap <C-u> <C-u>zz

" closing and saving
command W w
command Q q
command WQ wq
command Wq wq


